  <item>
    <title>Supporting Parents on the Journey to College</title>
    <link>https://www.collegeboard.org/membership/all-access/counseling-admissions-financial-aid-academic/supporting-parents-journey</link>
    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-image field-type-image field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; rel=&quot;&quot; resource=&quot;https://www.collegeboard.org/sites/default/files/styles/all_access_image_style/public/parent%20webinar.png?itok=f1X2Lb0V&quot;&gt;&lt;img typeof=&quot;foaf:Image&quot; src=&quot;https://www.collegeboard.org/sites/default/files/styles/all_access_image_style/public/parent%20webinar.png?itok=f1X2Lb0V&quot; alt=&quot;Supporting Parents on the Journey to College&quot; title=&quot;Supporting Parents on the Journey to College&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-author field-type-text field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;Adele Hazan, Senior Director, Communications &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-newsletter-tags field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/all-access-tags/parents&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;Parents&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/taxonomy/term/391&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;advanced placement&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/taxonomy/term/616&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;Admissions&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/all-access-tags/financial-aid&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;Financial Aid&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/all-access-tags/college-planning&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;College Planning&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/all-access-tags/webinars&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;webinars&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;The College Board is hosting a monthly webinar series to help parents support their children during the college planning process. Topics include preparing for the SAT test, learning about AP courses, applying for financial aid, and more. Each webinar will feature leaders from the College Board, our membership, and our partner organizations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We encourage you to share registration information with your local PTA, parents in your network, and beyond.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here’s a look at what’s coming up:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Introduction to Advanced Placement&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:40px&quot;&gt;Tuesday, August 23, 7-8:00 p.m. ET&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:40px&quot;&gt;Speakers:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-left:40px&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;Edward Biedermann, Executive Director, AP Outreach, College Board&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Gail Kaplan, Professor of Mathematics, Towson University&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Kelly Stromberg, AP Capstone Teacher, North Central High School&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:40px&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://collegeboardtraining.webex.com/collegeboardtraining/onstage/g.php?MTID=eb5e7d559d73e6db17f5eb9b0e36e7195&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Register&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Getting Ready for the SAT&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
