    <title>Board Chair Doug Christiansen Offers College Essay-Writing Tips</title>
    <link>https://www.collegeboard.org/membership/all-access/admissions/board-chair-doug-christiansen-offers-college-essay-writing-tips</link>
    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-image field-type-image field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; rel=&quot;&quot; resource=&quot;https://www.collegeboard.org/sites/default/files/styles/all_access_image_style/public/DChristiansen.jpg?itok=JGiTKpPQ&quot;&gt;&lt;img typeof=&quot;foaf:Image&quot; src=&quot;https://www.collegeboard.org/sites/default/files/styles/all_access_image_style/public/DChristiansen.jpg?itok=JGiTKpPQ&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-author field-type-text field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;College Board Communications &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-newsletter-tags field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/taxonomy/term/616&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;Admissions&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/taxonomy/term/586&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;Board of Trustees&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/all-access-tags/college-applications&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;college applications&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;To help students gear up for this year’s college application season, &lt;em&gt;NBC News&lt;/em&gt; published some personal essay-writing tips. Doug Christiansen, chair of the College Board&#039;s Board of Trustees, shared the following advice:  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; “The college essay is one of the only places on an application where a student can let the admissions committee hear their authentic voice and one of the only places for students to differentiate themselves from an ever-increasing pool of applicants, Doug Christiansen, Vice Provost for University Enrollment Affairs and Dean of Admissions and Financial Aid at Vanderbilt University told NBC News.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;‘Most highly selective schools, such as Vanderbilt University, are looking for students who have learned from a personal experience and then utilized that knowledge to somehow make a positive difference in the world around them,’ he said.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;‘Leadership during personally challenging times is important, but so is being part of a team working together to create something positive,’ he added. ‘At the end of the day, we want to know who you are and how your experiences have shaped you and the world around you.’”&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Read more tips on &lt;em&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.nbcnews.com/feature/college-game-plan/dreading-writing-your-college-application-essay-tips-pros-n616956&quot;&gt;NBC News&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span property=&quot;dc:title&quot; content=&quot;Board Chair Doug Christiansen Offers College Essay-Writing Tips&quot; class=&quot;rdf-meta element-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</description>
     <pubDate>Wed, 17 Aug 2016 19:40:38 +0000</pubDate>
 <dc:creator>ahexter</dc:creator>
